  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "Seamless 10GbE Connectivity",
      "text": "The Ubiquiti 10G Ethernet Adapter UACC‑Adapter‑RJ45‑USBC‑10GE) delivers ultra-fast network access through a compact, plug-and-play solution. Featuring a 10 GbE RJ45 port and a USB‑C interface, it allows seamless integration with modern laptops, desktops, and servers. Its polycarbonate and aluminum alloy enclosure ensures durability while keeping the design lightweight and portable. Compatible with Mac OS 14.2 and later, Windows 7/8/8.1/10/11 (32/64-bit), and Linux, it provides universal connectivity for a wide range of devices. The adapter supports Gigabit LAN for maximum flexibility and includes a LAN activity indicator for real-time network status. Operating in ambient temperatures from 5 °C to 45 °C, it’s ideal for professional environments. NDAA compliance and certifications (CE, FCC, IC, UKCA) ensure it meets rigorous global standards for performance and safety."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Reliable Performance",
      "text": "Engineered for high-performance networking, the UACC‑Adapter‑RJ45‑USBC‑10GE is the perfect solution for users requiring fast, wired Ethernet connections on devices with USB‑C ports. With full support for 10 Gbps data rates, it’s designed to handle bandwidth-intensive applications, from large file transfers to video conferencing and cloud access. Its lightweight construction makes it easy to carry, while robust materials ensure reliable operation in demanding environments. Installation is effortless—just connect and instantly upgrade your device’s networking capabilities without additional drivers. The adapter’s built-in LAN activity indicator keeps you informed of connection status, enhancing usability. Whether you’re setting up in an office, data center, or home workspace, this adapter delivers the speed and stability needed for modern networking demands."
    }
  ],
